Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:16.38,KARA-english,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I'll show you a world that shines in the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:21.64,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.72,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,There were another 23 victims yesterday, again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.72,0:01:32.82,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as the possibility of Kira being a student is put forward, the timing of the murders change to indicate that this isn't the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:35.69,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this means that Kira must have access to police information.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.25,0:01:42.91,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Now that L knows I'm somehow getting police information, without doubt, he'll use the police as a link to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:46.64,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,There's a human that's been following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:50.99,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I've got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:53.13,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to get rid of him as soon as possible, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:59.91,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami's eyes have the ability to see a person's name and life span, just by looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:02:00.80,Note,NOTE,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:00.92,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Also, {\alpha&HFF&}Shinigami have the ability to change the eyes of any human who finds their notebook, into the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Shinigami have the ability to change the eyes of any human who finds their notebook, {\alpha&HFF&}into the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Shinigami have the ability to change the eyes of any human who finds their notebook, into the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:11.34,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,The price for a Shinigami's eyes is... {\alpha&HFF&}half of your remaining life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The price for a Shinigami's eyes is... half of your remaining life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:20.03,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want to do, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:23.16,SIGN,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(353,333)}The Chase
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:26.52,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't seen Ryuk around lately, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:29.79,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,Was he serious about having dropped his Death Note on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:32.68,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been picked up by a human before he got to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:39.43,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,No way! If he did something like that, he'd be forced to watch over them until either the human dies, or the notebook is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:43.48,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. There's no way Ryuk could be bothered to do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:47.64,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I heard he's got two Death Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:50.60,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?! Why the hell has he got two?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.95,Default,Shinigami,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't understand the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:57.51,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,So, in order for me to acquire the eyes of a Shinigami, {\alpha&HFF&}I've got to give up half of my remaining life span... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:03:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in order for me to acquire the eyes of a Shinigami, I've got to give up half of my remaining life span... {\alpha&HFF&}right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in order for me to acquire the eyes of a Shinigami, I've got to give up half of my remaining life span... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:05.04,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so what do ya wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:06.37,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Have we got a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:10.73,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk.. {\alpha&HFF&}that deal is... out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk.. that deal is... {\alpha&HFF&}out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk.. that deal is... out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:14.52,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:28.57,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to create a new ideal world, free of criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:36.53,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,And I intend to reign as God of that new world for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:39.07,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,If the deal had involved increasing my life span, {alpha&HFF&}I might have considered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.95,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,But anything that decreases it isn't even worth discussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:44.45,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have thought that you'd already know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:49.40,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Well, I just wanted to tell you that the deal exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:53.65,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Thought I'd better tell you this sort of thing early on, so I don't have to put up with your complaints later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:57.27,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,You thought you'd better tell me this sort of thing "early on"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:59.20,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it already slightly late?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:02.38,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me this either as soon as we met, {\alpha&HFF&}or written it as part of the explanations in the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me this either as soon as we met, or written it as part of the explanations in the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:08.66,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Err.. I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:11.83,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't fear me in the slightest, even though I'm a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:16.42,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't try to suck up to me, and he keeps on relentlessly asking such probing questions of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:22.50,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:28.24,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else you should have told me beforehand, Ryuk the Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.22,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:32.12,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.16,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:35.86,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,A shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.93,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,If it was wings instead of eyes, {\alpha&HFF&}I might have seriously considered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was wings instead of eyes, I might have seriously considered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:44.27,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It seems quite fitting for a god to have wings and fly freely across the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:48.72,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's been man's dream since antiquity to be able to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:52.74,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,If you grew wings and flew around you'd stand out too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:55.65,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,The police would probably be able to catch you purely on that basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.10,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I was joking, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:02.85,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,With all the trading of eyes, wings or whatever, {\alpha&HFF&}I'd probably end up becoming a real Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all the trading of eyes, wings or whatever, I'd probably end up becoming a real Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:08.49,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Although, I guess that could be quite an interesting concept too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.56,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.57,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Even without doing anything like that, {\alpha&HFF&}you're already a worthy Shinigami, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without doing anything like that, you're already {\alpha&HFF&}a worthy Shinigami, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without doing anything like that, you're already a worthy Shinigami, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:21.20,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the World of Shinigami is rotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They live a vague and pointless existence, only taking human lives because they, themselves, are afraid to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:33.90,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,They no longer understand why they even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:37.34,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,There's probably no meaning in their existence at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:41.19,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to them, Light, {\alpha&HFF&}you're more of a Shinigami than they'll ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to them, Light, you're more of a Shinigami than they'll ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:46.33,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Well, by the sound of things, {\alpha&HFF&}I'm doing a lot more work than them, but I wouldn't want to be compared to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, by the sound of things, I'm doing a lot more work than them, {\alpha&HFF&}but I wouldn't want to be compared to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, by the sound of things, I'm doing a lot more work than them, but I wouldn't want to be compared to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:57.35,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,As a human, I'm using the Death Note to help humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:04.78,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,But it isn't like the World of Shinigami is of little importance to the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:07.33,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:08.86,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth. {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuk, even if Shinigami like you come down just once every hundred — no, thousand — years, the human world will change dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth. Ryuk, even if Shinigami like you come down just once every hundred{\alpha&HFF&} — no, thousand — years, the human world will change dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth. Ryuk, even if Shinigami like you come down just once every hundred — no, thousand — years, the human world will change dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:20.62,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,The existence of the World of Shinigami is extremely significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:22.19,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,R-really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:27.44,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,If the World of Shinigami is really as rotten as you say it is, Ryuk, {\alpha&HFF&}why don't you try changing things when you get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the World of Shinigami is really as rotten as you say it is, Ryuk, why don't you try changing things when you get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:33.45,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Light, {\alpha&HFF&}you're turning out to be quite the positive thinker..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, you're turning out to be quite the positive thinker..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:41.03,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:46.84,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be a positive thinker to think of using the Death Note to personally right the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:51.30,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:53.35,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.14,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:56.10,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,What do you "got"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:03.03,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured out how to obtain the name of my stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.64,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,What're you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.73,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be using the rules of the Death Note to my advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:13.91,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,"Should a cause of death be specified, a further 6 minutes and 40 seconds are granted to write any further details".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.23,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,First, {\alpha&HFF&}I'll need to test just how free I am to specify the details of the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll need to test just how free I am to specify the details of the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.42,MINOR SIGN,MINOR SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(354,387)}The next day
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.14,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:33.20,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,Another six prisoners?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.34,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,Due to heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:35.83,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:37.56,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:41.44,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,Three of them exhibited a pattern of behavior before death that we've never seen before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.35,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.31,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it wasn't just a normal heart attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:45.90,Default,Detective,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}The cause of death was definitely a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The cause of death was definitely a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:49.65,Default,Detective,0000,0000,0000,,But directly before it happened, {\alpha&HFF&}one of them cut his own finger and drew a strange picture on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But directly before it happened, one of them cut his own finger and drew a strange picture on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:57.33,Default,Detective,0000,0000,0000,,Another left an unexplainable note.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:02.87,Default,Detective,0000,0000,0000,,The third managed to escape and seems to have made the effort to run all the way to the staff toilets before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.00,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:15.46,Default,Watari,0000,0000,0000,,A few heart attack victims that acted slightly different from the usual have just been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:17.05,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Different from the usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:21.10,Default,Watari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending you the images of the text and picture they left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.02,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.63,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,This reads as though he's afraid of Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:32.49,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It could conceivably be merely the actions of a criminal, {\alpha&HFF&}but if Kira can control the time of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could conceivably be merely the actions of a criminal, but if Kira can control the time of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:38.98,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,What if Kira can also control the movements leading up to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.20,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,In which case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:44.27,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, {\alpha&HFF&}regarding the most recent victims, I'd like to request that no details regarding their deaths are released other than that they died of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, regarding the most recent victims, {\alpha&HFF&}I'd like to request that no details regarding their deaths are released other than that they died of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, regarding the most recent victims, I'd like to request that no details regarding their deaths are released other than that they died of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:55.99,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that Kira may be using these criminals to conduct some kind of test.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.87,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,And if that is the case, {\alpha&HFF&}we shouldn't give them any easy answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that is the case, we shouldn't give them any easy answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:03.09,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,I see..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:05.00,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:07.43,Default,Detective,0000,0000,0000,,Performing tests on criminals?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:08.55,Default,Detective,0000,0000,0000,,Cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:11.17,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,It seems as though they enjoy playing games with people's lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:13.61,Default,ChiefYagami,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:20.35,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira's really experimenting on criminals... {\alpha&HFF&}what's their objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira's really experimenting on criminals... what's their objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:31.31,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:36.65,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,The results of yesterday's six tests have already been entered into dad's computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:40.68,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note is even more useful than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:42.68,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,What d'ya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:47.11,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Having escaped, one of them ran to a toilet that I'd specified in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:51.44,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Another drew the exact picture that I'd drawn in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:55.90,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,And another wrote the same sentences that I wrote in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:10:00.45,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Those three did exactly what I intended them to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:05.27,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,For the remaining three, I purposely wrote circumstances that would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:07.09,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,First, {\alpha&HFF&}I wrote that the victim would die in an hour's time in front of the Eiffel Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I wrote that the victim would die in an hour's time in front of the Eiffel Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:14.93,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It's physically impossible for a prisoner in Japan to reach France in just an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:20.53,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, this doesn't actually happen, and the victim simply dies of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:26.51,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I wrote "Draws an exact picture of L's face on the wall" in the Death Note,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's impossible to draw somebody you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.60,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:33.04,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Lastly, I specified that the final victim should write, {\alpha&HFF&}"I know that L is suspicious of the police force".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lastly, I specified that the final victim should write, "I know that L is suspicious of the police force".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:43.42,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that this one might work, but it didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:51.81,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,If someone doesn't know a piece of information, they can't think of it, and so it'd be unnatural for that person to write it down, meaning they won't be able to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:55.43,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Death Note cannot accomplish the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:57.13,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,But, {\alpha&HFF&}if it's within the realistic limits of what they can do, I can control them as much as I like before they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:11:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if it's within the realistic limits of what they can do, I can control them as much as I like before they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:08.89,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,I've got that much, but what are ya trying to achieve, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:15.05,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,L and the police will never be able to guess my true objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:19.70,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,The famous detective will be too busy investigating the mystery of those pictures and messages...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:23.70,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Those completely meaningless "dying messages".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:31.27,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira is really using criminals as test subjects, it must be because they're about to begin something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:34.11,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,If they make a move now, {\alpha&HFF&}there's the possibility that their suspicious actions will be picked up by the FBI...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they make a move now, there's the possibility that their suspicious actions will be picked up by the FBI...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:40.08,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,But... {\alpha&HFF&}If there's another reason they're doing this, other than to run tests...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... If there's another reason they're doing this, other than to run tests...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:46.39,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a message in the drawings and text.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:48.93,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:52.56,Note,NOTE,0000,0000,0000,,The upper line reads "L, did you know?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:53.71,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it's finally time for the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:55.71,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Real deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:57.60,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use this drug addict.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:03.82,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, he attempted to rob a bank, but failed to take any money, and escaped by shooting employees and members of the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:07.66,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It's slightly last minute, but I'm sure it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.36,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try asking a few people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.65,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,"Try asking a few people"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:12.82,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. {\alpha&HFF&}Despite my appearance, I'm actually quite popular with the ladies, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Despite my appearance, I'm actually quite popular with the ladies, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:27.38,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,..Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:30.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Light?! Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:56.12,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,He's still following me. Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:13:00.17,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,If he wasn't, what I'm about to do would be pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.43,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:08.72,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,A date, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:09.43,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:11.91,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,However you look at it, it's just a normal date.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:15.47,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Even the guy that's following me can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:17.78,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,But it isn't just a "normal" date, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:21.07,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned something about knowing how to figure out your stalker's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.99,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you plan on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:25.76,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Ryuk? {\alpha&HFF&}Didn't you see what I wrote in the Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Ryuk? Didn't you see what I wrote in the Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.22,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}Otherwise it'd be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Otherwise it'd be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:34.99,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, just be patient and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.26,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. {\alpha&HFF&}Have you been waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Have you been waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.56,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No. Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:44.76,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I haven't been to Space Land since Junior High!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:48.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And we get to spend the entire day together, just the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:55.64,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,If he goes out on a weekday, he either goes to school or cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.87,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,On the odd day off, he goes on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:02.86,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,Seems pretty normal. An earnest final year exam student.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:06.14,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,Police Chief Yagami's son, Light - {\alpha&HFF&}no need for suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police Chief Yagami's son, Light - no need for suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:14.60,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just check his movements today, and then that'll be the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:24.67,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But Light, didn't you say that we weren't going to go out until the exams are over?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:28.06,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's okay, since I placed first in the national mock exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.47,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Eww, no need to be so smug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:04.80,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:05.80,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:11.34,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Seven customers, excluding him... {\alpha&HFF&}in that case, everything should proceed smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven customers, excluding him... in that case, everything should proceed smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:19.09,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking over this bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:22.38,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,A bus hi-jack?! {\alpha&HFF&}At a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bus hi-jack?! At a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:27.74,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down! I'll kill anyone who dares to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:33.33,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, driver! D'ya know the phone number of the Space Land offices?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:34.02,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Call 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:34.74,Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.70,Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,This is driver Sasaki, of bus number 124.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:41.00,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Tell 'em what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:42.01,Default,Driver,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}I've been hi-hacked by a man with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've been hi-hacked by a man with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:46.21,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Give it 'ere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.02,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,You heard what's going on? {\alpha&HFF&}Now, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard what's going on? Now, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:59.46,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,I want a woman in a car to bring yesterday's takings to the bus stop two stops away from Space Land before this bus gets there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:04.49,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,If you call the police, or try anything funny, I'll kill every single person on this bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:19.75,LongNote,NOTE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}Yuri-chan, don't worry; it's okay. \NI'll find an opportunity to disarm him. \NMy father's a police officer and I've \Nlearnt how to counter-attack such a scenario. \NHe looks small and relatively weak. \NI'm stronger than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:17.75,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri-chan, don't worry; it's okay. I'll find an opportunity to disarm him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:20.09,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, it's too dangerous. Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:21.87,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,If it comes to that, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:26.55,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, you don't need to communicate in writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:30.05,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,The noise of the bus is enough to cover up hushed conversations from the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:35.89,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any proof that you're not an accomplice to this crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:37.21,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,A-{\alpha&HFF&}an accomplice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-an accomplice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:40.47,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fairly common practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:46.98,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit fools us into thinking he's alone, but secretly plants an accomplice at the back, just in case anything goes wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:49.39,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:52.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, no way, it can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:52.79,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}I don't have a choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't have a choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.86,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Yagami Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:59.99,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,If he was, then he'd be able to kill the culprit with a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.75,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my proof. Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.81,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,FBI!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:11.88,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,So that's who L's been using to investigate the Japanese police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.24,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,His name is {\alpha&HFF&}Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Ray {\alpha&HFF&}Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:19.52,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I'll trust you, {\alpha&HFF&}and for the time being I won't question what an FBI agent is doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll trust you, and for the time being I won't question what an FBI agent is doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:25.65,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:26.39,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:30.23,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,So if it comes to that, I'll be relying on you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:30.72,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:34.99,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up! Do ya wanna die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:36.83,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,That man! {\alpha&HFF&}He was on the Japanese news two days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man! He was on the Japanese news two days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:44.42,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,He robbed a bank, killed three people, and then fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:47.04,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,He's extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.40,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. {\alpha&HFF&}He'll never shoot us with that gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. He'll never shoot us with that gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.88,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, you! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.68,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,What's on that bit of paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.09,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--! {\alpha&HFF&}You passing notes around to try plotting against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--! You passing notes around to try plotting against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:05.03,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! {\alpha&HFF&}If he finds that note from before... he'll realize that we're waiting for an opportunity to overpower him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! If he finds that note from before... {\alpha&HFF&}he'll realize that we're waiting for an opportunity to overpower him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! If he finds that note from before... he'll realize that we're waiting for an opportunity to overpower him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.98,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Just arrangements for a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.33,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,What a load of crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:18.36,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.21,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.29,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,You! The guy right at the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:33.46,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:36.01,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Since when have you been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.01,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? {\alpha&HFF&}You talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:42.30,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,You can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.51,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! {\alpha&HFF&}I-I'll shoot you, you freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! I-{\alpha&HFF&}I'll shoot you, you freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! I-I'll shoot you, you freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:48.66,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.. he's hallucinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.02,Default,RayePenber,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.57,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:19:01.41,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,That note with the arrangements for the date was written on paper from the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:06.71,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,And he made this guy touch it, so this guy's the only one who's able to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:08.46,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:09.92,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:13.95,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:17.30,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I'm a Shinigami, so things like that won't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:33.37,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,"Those who touch the Death Note are able to see me."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:36.91,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,"I will always have to follow Light around."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.81,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,"Shinigami won't die just by being shot."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:42.58,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,These are all things I've told Light in the past, {\alpha&HFF&}and this is just the kind of practical application I'd expect from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are all things I've told Light in the past, and this is just the kind of practical application I'd expect from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:52.83,Default,Ryuk,0000,0000,0000,,And he's managed to use this hi-jacking to get the name of the guy that's been following him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:56.46,Default,Hijacker,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.00,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly 11:45.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:28.00,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Everything went according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:31.39,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,Oosoreda Kiichirou... {\alpha&HFF&}death by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oosoreda Kiichirou... death by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:49.10,Note,NOTE,0000,0000,0000,,The text in the background says the same as Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:43.03,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Boards the 11:31-bus to Space Land from the bus station at the east entrance to the park, with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:50.98,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Appears to have some out-of-this-world type of hallucination and empties his gun towards it. Disembarks from the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:56.19,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately afterwards; same day; 11:45 - dies in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:04.00,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note never fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:10.80,Default,Light,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn next... {\alpha&HFF&}Ray Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn next... Ray Penber.
